{"tid":613398,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"自閉兒遭父女友性侵 父辯稱：想矯正同性戀","createTime":"2018-04-01T15:54:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-02T00:49:12.000Z","uid":136553,"like":3,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"15481a3366e8e3a7dfaf3834f3c96bc7303fc0b4","tid":613398,"uid":136553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:54:36.000Z","msg":"2018-03-31 14:17<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕美國阿拉巴馬州一名父親柯爾（Sean Cole ）因懷疑自己11歲患有自閉症的兒子是同性戀，竟要求自己20歲的女友強行性侵兒子，以「矯正」性向。<br />\n<br />\n綜合外媒報導，一名29歲父親柯爾發現自己兒子跟另一名男孩過度親近，懷疑其為同性戀，便要求自己女友摩爾（Khadeijah Moore）性侵兒子。柯爾接受檢察官調查時更表示，不希望自己兒子變成同性戀，想矯正其性向才犯行。而檢察官多斯特（Tim Douthit）指出，男孩至今仍無法理解父親為什麼這麼做，甚至認為一定是自己做錯什麼。<br />\n<br />\n這名男孩即將要滿13歲，目前跟母親住在喬治亞州。「他始終認為，自己是個壞人，這真的讓人很心碎」多斯特表示，處理過非常多件兒童性犯罪，但這是第一次碰到的案例。父親柯爾目前被關押在麥迪遜縣（Madison County）監獄中，而其女友至今仍在逃亡中，最終審判將在5月出爐。"},{"pid":"e234f86181bcdf0bf911adc9d42cdfca54cd4e09","tid":613398,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lgbtqnation-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/assets/2018/03/Sean-Cole-Khadeijah-Moore-500x263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flgbtqnation-assets.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fassets%2F2018%2F03%2FSean-Cole-Khadeijah-Moore-500x263.jpg&h=80a2afb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f241e622111285644da7714ddf2d433c947044b1","tid":613398,"uid":62409,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"e234f86181bcdf0bf911adc9d42cdfca54cd4e09","tid":613398,"uid":76115,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:55:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://lgbtqnation-assets.s3.amazonaws.com/assets/2018/03/Sean-Cole-Khadeijah-Moore-500x263.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Flgbtqnation-assets.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fassets%2F2018%2F03%2FSean-Cole-Khadeijah-Moore-500x263.jpg&h=80a2afb9&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-01T15:56:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://media.giphy.com/media/X4YqmJEl6wJoY/200.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"http